<h4 id="л¬ём„ң-м°ҫкё°">л¬ём„ң м°ҫкё°</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">filter_doc</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
